{"tid":36487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族黨　陳浩天周浩輝　在台灣　遭　愛字頭組織　襲擊","createTime":"2016-12-12T17:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T23:32:26.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa003027aa3bd0914ae89326cecd5c10798a144","tid":36487,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F580288865503405&d=CtI4Ci5E5sIe5Fgc2Jc1F6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=1cf99eef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405</a><br />\n<br />\n【召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝於台灣遇襲】<br />\n敝黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝今日(12/12)晚上於台北一餐廳接受記者訪問後，當二人準備離開餐廳，多人即衝前施襲，並在場高叫「搞港獨台獨」、「漢奸賣國」。民族黨強烈譴責施襲者及其背後相關團體。二人並無大礙，現於台北中正區一警察局錄取口供，稍後將進一步交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/jUwQtA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjUwQtA&h=28477f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/pcb.580288865503405/580288148836810/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.580288865503405%2F580288148836810%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=CtI4Ci5E5sIe5Fgc2Jc1F6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=2f003c0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/pcb.580288865503405/580288148836810/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/fQ9mga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfQ9mga&h=aac709e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWilliam Liang:<br />\n這個就是愛國同心會的張秀葉，嫁來台灣，鼓吹統一，常在101拿五星旗鬧事打人。"},{"pid":"d2272e6c2b93700b3082e46a6dd92d5613634c5b","tid":36487,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"好彩冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0c1836c3c70fd81d07affbbd33f9aba42b8266","tid":36487,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:45:02.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd42d39a4f4297b3fc9e17e95c2a9bacf4a42c9c","tid":36487,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F580288865503405&d=CtI4Ci5E5sIe5Fgc2Jc1F6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=1cf99eef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405</a><br />\n<br />\n【召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝於台灣遇襲】<br />\n敝黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝今日(12/12)晚上於台北一餐廳接受記者訪問後，當二人準備離開餐廳，多人即衝前施襲，並在場高叫「搞港獨台獨」、「漢奸賣國」。民族黨強烈譴責施襲者及其背後相關團體。二人並無大礙，現於台北中正區一警察局錄取口供，稍後將進一步交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/jUwQtA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjUwQtA&h=28477f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/pcb.580288865503405/580288148836810/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.580288865503405%2F580288148836810%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=CtI4Ci5E5sIe5Fgc2Jc1F6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=2f003c0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/pcb.580288865503405/580288148836810/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/fQ9mga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfQ9mga&h=aac709e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWilliam Liang:<br />\n這個就是愛國同心會的張秀葉，嫁來台灣，鼓吹統一，常在101拿五星旗鬧事打人。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首頁即時報紙體育娛樂評論時尚3C汽車食譜地產<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n快訊<br />\n<br />\n今晚冷氣團來襲！ 週四低溫下探13度<br />\n<br />\n社會新聞<br />\n<br />\n辱警張秀葉 中國嫁來台<br />\n2015-03-07<br />\n<br />\n〔記者吳張鴻、吳政峰／台北報導〕愛國同心會總幹事張秀葉、成員遇港生，昨日下午因辱罵員警被法辦。據媒體報導，張秀葉是中國配偶，曾自述遭受家暴；遇港生則曾揚言要殺害前總統陳水扁一家人，而被判刑入獄。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的張秀葉，多年前接受公視導演蔡崇隆採訪，錄製「中國新娘在台灣」的紀錄片，自稱1992年嫁來台灣，因家暴而訴請離婚；但前夫反駁，指當年張女登報徵婚，2人多次通信後結婚，婚後張卻不履行同居義務，最後對簿公堂。<br />\n<br />\n遇港生曾揚言要追殺陳水扁一家人，被判刑1年10個月，2年前出獄，又跑到台北市日僑學校噴紅漆，揚言「殺日本人」，被士林地院依恐嚇公眾罪，判處4個月，得易科罰金。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/paper/860693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F860693&d=CtI4Ci5E5sIe5Fgc2Jc1F6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=b0f0d7f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F860693&h=76026069\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/paper/860693</a>"},{"pid":"739e2d8c467e6b4664060ea75f03878ba4d83a81","tid":36487,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb0ed53f8528f6a03631331df174d6d23620283","tid":36487,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:12:33.000Z","msg":"又係脫離中國後又話愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f62b962aa3e0b99a56e7c95e54bb1470d20e42","tid":36487,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愛國同心會唔好入台灣數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fa9155bd018f25965d273c28a483152eb3